hadith.english-text:
It was reported from Abu An-Nadr, from Abu Salama bin
'Abdur Rahman, from 'Aishah, that she said: "I used to be asleep
while my legs would be in the front of the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ)
while he was praying during the night. When he wanted to prostrate,
he would prod my feet, so I would pull them up, and he would
prostrate.
